      "name": "Phase 1: Pre-Launch",
      "content": "<p>1. C-Corp formation</p><p>2. Draft TOS & Privacy Policy</p><p>3. Run license audit</p><p>4. Review Google Gemini API terms</p><p>5. Get insurance quotes</p>",
